## **1. Log Parameters in Function** ‚≠ê *Most common*

```csharp
public void UpdateBrightness(float newBrightness)
{
    Debug.Log($"[LanternGame] UpdateBrightness called with: {newBrightness}");

    brightness = Mathf.Clamp01(newBrightness);

    Debug.Log($"[LanternGame] Brightness clamped to: {brightness}");
}
```

